{"word":"G877 - ἀφροσύνη - aphrosýnē - af-ros-oo'-nay - Folly","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀφροσύνη</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>aphrosýnē"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>af-ros-oo'-nay"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Folly"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"மதிகேடு, புத்தியீனம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"foolishness, folly, senselessness, thoughtlessness, recklessness"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G878 - ἄφρων - áphrōn - af'-rone/878\">G878</a>; <i>senselessness</i>, that is, (euphemistically) <i>egotism</i>; (morally) <i>recklessness:</i> - folly, foolishly (-ness)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5424 - φρήν - phrḗn - frane/5424\">G5424</a>, <a href=\"#/G5426 - φρονέω - phronéō - fron-eh'-o/5426\">G5426</a>, <a href=\"#/G5427 - φρόνημα - phrónēma - fron'-ay-mah/5427\">G5427</a>, <a href=\"#/G5428 - φρόνησις - phrónēsis - fron'-ay-sis/5428\">G5428</a>, <a href=\"#/G5429 - φρόνιμος - phrónimos - fron'-ee-mos/5429\">G5429</a>, <a href=\"#/G5430 - φρονίμως - phronímōs - fron-im'-oce/5430\">G5430</a>, <a href=\"#/G877 - ἀφροσύνη - aphrosýnē - af-ros-oo'-nay/877\">G877</a>, <a href=\"#/G878 - ἄφρων - áphrōn - af'-rone/878\">G878</a>"}]}